{
  "stem": "11205.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Only food, we took it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We left everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because it-- it was-- you know, it wasn't the military's object.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, every morning, we used to go out in the forest, and the airplanes used to fly over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was-- and we made up that in the forest that my father was sitting with the two children, my mother separate so in case-- we-- we were under this impression that the airplane could spot us.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, that's how I-- I-- I was terrified.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was about 10 days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then it was quiet, and they-- the war-- we came back-- was ahead of Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came back, my-- it-- my mother had beautiful plants, a parapet in-- in the-- it's a-- on the windows, and all of the plants were dead.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we found out that just a bomb, which didn't explode, was over the fence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what-- otherwise, the house would have been-- and all of the windows were-- have all of the ceilings have been.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we came back [? ahead of ?] Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother went out in the market, and that was-- and she prepared-- [CRYING]",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember what she made potatoes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[CRYING] And then, they went off to-- to shul.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I was sitting home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the last holiday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember they-- they went to shul.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we went to our friend, you know, myself and the two younger, to be close to the shul, and that in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A big shooting came that the Germans were already not far, and that was the last of them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and nobody came, no Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Polish army was dissolved, and nothing.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
